《星际争霸》发行于1998年，一年内即售出了150万套<ref name="1998sales">{{en}}{{cite web |title=StarCraft Named #1 Seller in 1998 |publisher=IGN |date=1999-01-20 |url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/066/066492p1.html |accessdate=2006-08-19 |archive-date=2008-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080204181704/http://pc.ign.com/articles/066/066492p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成为当年销量最好的[[电脑游戏|PC游戏]]。截至2009年2月，《星际争霸》的总销量超过1100万套<ref name="bestselling" />。游戏的发行同时使[[战网|Battle.net]]上多人对战的用户数量增长至了原先的8倍<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Blizzard's Battle.net Remains Largest Online Game Service in the World; Battle.net Dominates Online Gaming Industry With 2.1 Million Active Users; Korea Becomes World's No. 1 Market |publisher=Business Wire |date=1999-02-04 |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0EIN/is_1999_Feb_4/ai_53706429 |accessdate=2008-07-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120529182015/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0EIN/is_1999_Feb_4/ai_53706429/ |archivedate=2012-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；《星际争霸》因而成为最流行的联机对战游戏之一<ref name="thenewyorktimes">{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/05/21/technology/21warcraft.html |title=To the Glee of South Korean Fans, a Game's Sequel Is Announced |accessdate=2008-01-09 |author=Schiesel, Seth |date=2007-05-21 |publisher=New York Times |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124031837/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/05/21/technology/21warcraft.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《星际争霸》获得了媒体的大量好评。许多评论家认为，尽管游戏或许没能跳出当今大多数[[即时战略游戏|即时战略游戏]]的惯用模式，但在當時，它无疑是同类游戏中最優秀的之一<ref name="GSpot" /><ref name="GamePro" />。此外，大多数评论家还称赞了游戏三个截然不同的种族的设计，称其不仅跳出了以往游戏两个相似阵营的设计，并且在平衡性上也做得非常出色<ref name="ignr" />。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]赞扬道其“避开了那个困扰着每个同类型游戏的问题”，以及“定义了这一类型的游戏，并使此后的所有[[即时战略游戏|即时战略游戏]]皆遵从这一标准”<ref name="GSpot" />。IGN特别强调，《星际争霸》可谓史上最佳的即时战略游戏之一<ref name="ignr" />。评论家同样赞扬了游戏故事的设定，以及其呈现方式<ref name="ignr" />。游戏的音效和配音特别得到了好评，GameSpot在随后称赞其是当时的十大最佳游戏音效之一<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/features/tenspot_voiceacting/page6.html |title=The Best Voice Acting in Games: ''StarCraft'' |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |first=James |last=Cheung |accessdate=2008-09-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004214523/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/tenspot_voiceacting/page6.html |archivedate=2013-10-04 }}</ref>。多人联机部分也得到了积极的评价。《星际争霸》曾荣获数个奖项，包括[[IGN|IGN]]与GameSpot颁发的“史上最佳游戏”奖<ref name="GspotAward" /><ref>{{en}}{{cite web | title = IGN's Top 100 Games | publisher = IGN | date = 2003-01-01 | url = http://top100.ign.com/2003/1-10.html | accessdate = 2006-08-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5mqeaoEzJ?url=http://top100.ign.com/2003/1-10.html | archivedate = 2010年1月17日 | df =  }}</ref>。暴雪表示，《星际争霸》总计荣获37个奖项，包括2006年初[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]Metreon购物中心举办的“{{link-en|游戏巡礼|Walk of Game}}”活动中的一枚星章<ref name="awardss"/>。

尽管在当时倍受好评，《星际争霸》的绘图和音效并不能与后期的游戏相提并论<ref name="ignr" />。而游戏中的[[人工智能|人工智能]]寻径系统也遭到了批评。{{Link-en|PC Zone}}批评开发者无法开发出一个有效率的寻径系统，称这是“在即时战略游戏中最容易激怒玩家的部分”<ref name="PCZ" />。有些评论家也批评了游戏允许玩家快攻（rush）的设计<ref name="GameRev" />，因此暴雪在此后的游戏补丁中两次调整了平衡性，限制了快攻战术的使用。

[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]版本的《星际争霸64》得到的分数普遍不如原版，并被批评了其粗劣的画质。但评论家同样肯定了高效率的控制界面，以及得以保留的高品质音效<ref name="GameProN64" /><ref name="GSpotN64" /><ref name="IGNN64" />。

== 游戏文化 ==

《星际争霸》不断得到各种佳评，在《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》评选的“史上百佳游戏”中名列第37位<ref name="Edge">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6231&Itemid=2&limit=1&limitstart=6 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080202064950/http://www.next-gen.biz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6231&Itemid=2&limit=1&limitstart=6 |archivedate=2008-02-02 |title=Top 100 Games |publisher=''[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]'' |date=2007-07-02 |accessdate=2008-05-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。由于极高的流行度，《星际争霸》打破了《[[吉尼斯世界纪录大全|吉尼斯世界纪录大全]]》中的三项纪录：“销量最高的PC即时战略游戏”、“职业联赛收入最高的游戏”、“比赛观众最多的游戏”<ref>{{en}}{{cite book|title=Guinness World Records Gamer's Edition|publisher=Hit Entertainment|year=2008|isbn=9781904994206}}</ref>。

此外，《星际争霸》曾经进入过真正的星际空间。在1999年的[[航天飞机|航天飞机任务]][[STS-96|STS-96]]中，美国[[宇航员|宇航员]]{{Link-en|丹尼尔·巴利|Daniel T. Barry}}将一套《星际争霸》带入了太空。这套游戏环绕[[地球|地球]]153圈后返回地面，现收藏于美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的[[暴雪娛樂|暴雪娱乐]]总部<ref name="SCSpace">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://blizzard.com/us/starcraft/sis/ |title=''StarCraft'' In Space |publisher=[[暴雪娛樂|Blizzard Entertainment]] |accessdate=2008-04-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080313091642/http://www.blizzard.com/us/starcraft/sis/ |archivedate=2008-03-13 }}</ref>。《星际争霸》还被用于进行学术研究。2009年初，[[柏克萊加州大學|柏克萊加州大學]]开办了一个预备课程，通过游戏来进行战略和理论研究<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://blog.wired.com/games/2009/01/uc-berkeley-int.html|title=U.C. Berkeley Now Offers ''StarCraft'' Class|publisher=[[Wired_News|Wired News]]|first=Earnest|last=Cavalli|date=2009-01-29|accessdate=2009-03-25|archive-date=2009-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406035750/http://blog.wired.com/games/2009/01/uc-berkeley-int.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 职业联赛 ===
{{main|星际争霸职业联赛}}

《星际争霸》在[[大韩民国|韩国]]极受欢迎，销量超过450万套<ref name="usatoday">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2007-05-21-starcraft2-peek_N.htm |title=South Korean gamers get a sneak peek at 'StarCraft II' |accessdate=2008-01-09 |author=Olsen, Kelly |date=2007-05-21 |publisher=[[今日美國|USA Today]] |archive-date=2008-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080929124905/http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2007-05-21-starcraft2-peek_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并成功发展出了完整的职业联赛制度。职业玩家在韩国属于社会名流，并在三个专门的电视台上进行现场对抗<ref name="lim">{{en}}{{cite web| author = Evers, Marco| title = The boys with the flying fingers: South Korea Turns PC Gaming into a Spectator Sport| publisher = Der Spiegel| date = 2006-02-06| url = http://www.spiegel.de/international/spiegel/0,1518,399476,00.html| accessdate = 2006-08-19| archive-date = 2012-02-14| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120214122431/http://www.spiegel.de/international/spiegel/0,1518,399476,00.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。职业星际选手可以获得电视台的签约、赞助以及比赛奖金。最著名的一位星际选手[[林遥焕|林遥焕]]（Slayer_'Boxer'）拥有超过50万人的爱好者俱乐部<ref name="pop">{{cite web| author = Cho, Kevin| title = Samsung, SK Telecom, Shinhan Sponsor South Korean Alien Killers| publisher = Bloomberg.com| date = 2006-01-15| url = http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=email_us&refer=asia&sid=a2JvzciDnpB4| accessdate = 2006-08-18| archive-date = 2015-11-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151105123118/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=email_us&refer=asia&sid=a2JvzciDnpB4| dead-url = no}}</ref>；唯一可以与Boxer抗衡的神族选手{{Link-ko|林胜春|임성춘}}（IntoTheRain），被称为God Of The High Templar和Greatest Ones of Protoss<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| title = IntoTheRain| publisher = Teamliquid| url = http://wiki.teamliquid.net/starcraft/IntoTheRain| accessdate = 2013-10-15| archive-date = 2017-12-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171204142227/http://wiki.teamliquid.net/starcraft/IntoTheRain| dead-url = no}}</ref>；同期顶尖的虫族选手[[洪榛浩|洪榛浩]]（Yellow）被称为Storm Zerg<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| title = YellOw| publisher = Teamliquid| url = http://wiki.teamliquid.net/starcraft/YellOw| accessdate = 2013-10-15| archive-date = 2017-12-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171209192034/http://wiki.teamliquid.net/starcraft/YellOw| dead-url = no}}</ref>；而另一位选手{{Link-ko|李允烈|이윤열}}（NaDa）则表示在2005年的各大赛事中收获了20万[[美元|美元]]<ref name="fans">{{en}}{{cite web|author=Rossignol, Jim |title=Sex, Fame and PC Baangs: How the Orient plays host to PC gaming’s strangest culture |publisher=PC Gamer |date=2005-04-01 |url=http://rossignol.cream.org/?p=284 |accessdate=2006-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060202060802/http://rossignol.cream.org/?p=284 |archivedate=2006-02-02 }}</ref>。

=== 小说 ===
{{main|星际争霸系列#相关小说|l1=星际争霸系列小说}}

《星际争霸》的故事情节被改编成为了数部小说。第一部《起义》（''Uprising''）由暴雪员工米琪·奈尔森所作，出版于2000年12月，作为了《星际争霸》剧情的前传<ref name="UprisingSS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780743418980|title=''StarCraft: Uprising'' (eBook)|publisher=Simon & Schuster|accessdate=2009-07-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090708135242/http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780743418980|archivedate=2009-07-08}}</ref>。另外两部——杰夫·格鲁伯所作的《利伯蒂的远征》（''Liberty's Crusade''）<ref name="LibertySS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780671041489|title=''StarCraft: Liberty's Crusade'' (Mass Market Paperback)|publisher=Simon & Schuster|accessdate=2009-07-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090708133138/http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780671041489|archivedate=2009-07-08}}</ref>和艾伦·罗森堡的《刀锋女王》（''Queen of Blades''）<ref name="QueenSS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780743471336 |title=''StarCraft: Queen of Blades'' (Mass Market Paperback) |publisher=Simon & Schuster |accessdate=2009-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327034125/http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780743471336 |archivedate=2009-03-27 }}</ref>——则通过了不同的视角讲述了游戏内容。在2007年的[[暴雪嘉年华|BlizzCon]]上，《星际争霸》剧情的原作者克里斯·梅森希望能将《星际争霸》和《母巢之战》的全部剧情改编为小说。此后的小说，如加百列·麦斯塔创作的《萨尔娜迦之影》（''Shadow of Xel'Naga''）<ref name="ShadowSS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780671041496 |title=''StarCraft: Shadow of the Xel'Naga'' (Mass Market Paperback) |publisher=Simon & Schuster |accessdate=2009-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829185754/http://books.simonandschuster.com/9780671041496 |archivedate=2009-08-29 }}</ref>和《黑暗圣堂传奇》（''The Dark Templar Saga''）<ref name="Golden1">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.blizzplanet.com/blog/comments/starcraft_dark_templar_trilogy_-_book_one_firstborn_qa_with_christie_golden/ |title=''StarCraft: The Dark Templar Saga'' trilogy interview with Christie Golden |date=2007-04-02 |accessdate=2009-07-18 |publisher=Blizzplanet |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mqeb6vVD?url=http://www.blizzplanet.com/blog/comments/starcraft_dark_templar_trilogy_-_book_one_firstborn_qa_with_christie_golden/ |archivedate=2010-01-17 }}</ref>则扩充了剧情主线，并建立了《[[星际争霸II|星际争霸II]]》的故事设定。

=== 桌上游戏 ===

以《星际争霸》中的人物角色和兵种形象为原型，ToyCom公司生产了许多的[[仿真玩具人|仿真玩具人]]和可收藏的雕像<ref name="IGNSCtoys">{{en}}{{cite web| url=http://uk.pc.ign.com/articles/064/064948p1.html| title="Blizzard tackles toys"| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2007-07-08| date=September 1998| archive-date=2009-02-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203095527/http://uk.pc.ign.com/articles/064/064948p1.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>{{link-en|科学塑料模型|Academy Plastic Model}}公司同样按照1:30的[[比例尺|比例尺]]生产了许多模型玩具，包括人族的机枪兵<ref name="marinemodel">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hobbyoutlets.com/acy/2012.htm |title=1/30 scale Terran marine model by Academy |publisher=Hobby Outlet |accessdate=2007-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051213212503/http://hobbyoutlets.com/acy/2012.htm |archivedate=2005-12-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和虫族的刺蛇<ref name="hydramodel">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hobbyoutlets.com/acy/2017.htm |title=1/30 scale Zerg hydralisk model by Academy |publisher=Hobby Outlet |accessdate=2007-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051221172321/http://hobbyoutlets.com/acy/2017.htm |archivedate=2005-12-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，暴雪娱乐还与{{link-en|幻想飞行游戏|Fantasy Flight Games}}合作了一款[[星际争霸桌上游戏|星际争霸桌上游戏]]，包含了更加丰富的《星际争霸》角色塑像<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| author = Wilson, Kevin| title = Playtest in Minneapolis at the Source on 6/16/06| work = Boardgame Geek| date = 2006-06-13| url = http://www.boardgamegeek.com/thread/113938| accessdate = 2006-08-19| archive-date = 2011-08-24| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/61AZPEjX3?url=http://www.boardgamegeek.com/thread/113938/playtest-in-minneapolis-at-the-source-on-61606| dead-url = no}}</ref>；并授权[[威世智|威世智]]公司出品了一个基于{{link-en|Alternity}}的[[電子角色扮演遊戲|RPG]]游戏《[[星际争霸：探险|星际争霸：探险]]》<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/2451490.html |title=Starcraft Adventures in the Works |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=1999-04-01 |accessdate=2009-07-21}}</ref>。

